  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Recruitment Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>GREEN Employment Agency</strong> is dedicated and committed to the cause of making positive impact to the lives of our candidates, employers and society we operate in. Our core values are \"<strong>Compassion, Accountability, Passion, Teamwork, Adaptability, Integrity, Novelty\".</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>RESPONSIBILITY:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handles and follows through sales leads/ enquiries</li>\n  <li>Sourcing and screening of candidates</li>\n  <li>Employer - candidate matching based on requirements and needs</li>\n  <li>Closure of sales and meet sales target</li>\n  <li>Working with operation team to fulfil sales orders</li>\n  <li>Provides consistently excellent customer service before and after sales</li>\n  <li>Customer handling and complaint management</li>\n  <li>Comply to all applicable laws and regulations</li>\n  <li>Additional responsibility to manage suppliers, and to screen candidates and check documents of candidates.</li>\n  <li>Other duties and responsibilities as assigned by company</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma/ Degree in any field</li>\n  <li>Possession of Certificate of Employment Intermediary (CEI) is highly advantageous</li>\n  <li>Competent in Microsoft Office Softwares (minimally Word, Excel, Outlook, Powerpoint).</li>\n  <li>Multi-lingual to deal with candidates from different nationalities (e.g. Burmese, Indonesian, Filipino). Some of them especially first timers have limited command of English.</li>\n  <li>Enjoys engaging and dealing with different stakeholders including employers, candidates, suppliers, teammates &amp; etc.</li>\n  <li>Empathetic and sincere as this is a people centric industry</li>\n  <li>Be professional in learning and continuously equip oneself with the necessary skills and knowledge to perform</li>\n  <li>Open and sensitive to people with different cultures and backgrounds</li>\n  <li>Observe and internalise company core values at work</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
